{"title":"草原·奔马","authors":["哈斯乌拉"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原·奔马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（蒙古族哈斯乌拉）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗乌拉山麓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾掩埋一片永恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有成熟的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有收获的时令"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有那丛鹅黄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汲着我的思念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萌着岁月的蹒跚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锡林郭勒河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"润着无声的渴盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍老的河岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍是吻别的歌声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一代雏鹰张翼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衔着风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衔着雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衔着一如昨日的黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勒勒车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于压弯了夜的悠长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当草原骤然扬蹄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塑成奔马的造型"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的青春倏然跃上马背"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找那不该荒芜的永恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒙古包"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在银屏上为五洲璀璨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大草原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞荡着牧人面红耳赤的争辩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从成吉思汗射落雕鹏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到仰望人造卫星升天……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：内蒙古自治区文联）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}